⟦ Node.js process FFI Type Declarations

  Provides typed FFI declarations for the Node.js process module.
  Import this module to get compile-time type checking for process operations.

  Example:
    i stdlib::ffiNodeProcess
    λgetWorkingDir()=>String=process.cwd()
⟧

e process:{
  cwd:λ()=>String,
  exit:λ(Int)=>Unit
}
